PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FThe two countries held hours of
OL,7,Findirect negotiations in Geneva on
OL,8,FThursday, with the Omani foreign
OL,9,Fminister, who mediated the talks,
OL,10,Fsaying there had been "significant
OL,11,Fprogress".
OL,13,FBadr al-Busaidi said technical talks
OL,14,Finvolving lower-level representatives
OL,15,Fwould continue next week in Vienna,
OL,16,Fthe home of the International Atomic
OL,17,FEnergy Agency. The United Nations'
OL,18,Fatomic watchdog likely would be
OL,19,Fcritical in any deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FIran was represented at the talks by
OL,7,Fits foreign minister, Abbas Araghchi,
OL,8,Fwhile Steve Witkoff, a billionaire
OL,9,Freal estate developer and friend of
OL,10,FTrump who serves as a special Mideast
OL,11,Fenvoy, headed up the US delegation
OL,12,Fwith the president's son-in-law, Jared
OL,13,FKushner.
OL,15,FThe discussions come as the US has
OL,16,Famassed a fleet of aircraft and
OL,17,Fwarships in the region, with the US
OL,18,Fpresident having threatened to attack
OL,19,Fthe Islamic Republic if no deal on its
OL,20,Fnuclear programme is reached.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FBut just before the talks ended,
OL,7,FIranian state television reported that
OL,8,FTehran was determined to continue
OL,9,Fenriching uranium, rejected proposals
OL,10,Fto transfer it abroad and sought the
OL,11,Flifting of international sanctions,
OL,12,Findicating it was not prepared to meet
OL,13,FTrump's demands.
OL,15,FThe president wants a deal to
OL,16,Fconstrain Iran's nuclear programme,
OL,17,Fand he sees an opportunity while the
OL,18,Fcountry is struggling at home with
OL,19,Fgrowing dissent following nationwide
OL,20,Fprotests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FIran also hopes to avert war, but
OL,7,Fmaintains it has the right to enrich
OL,8,Furanium and does not want to discuss
OL,9,Fother issues, like its long-range
OL,10,Fmissile programme or support for armed
OL,11,Fgroups like Hamas and Hezbollah.
OL,13,FIn an interview with Iranian state
OL,14,Ftelevision, the country's foreign
OL,15,Fminister said the talks with the US
OL,16,Fwere some of its "most intense and
OL,17,Flongest rounds of negotiations".
OL,19,FAraghchi offered no specifics but said
OL,20,F"what needs to happen has been clearly
OL,21,Fspelt out from our side."
OL,26,@xD@ROU|D@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
