OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FThe White House did not immediately
OL,7,Frespond to a request from AP, ITV
OL,8,FNews' US partner, for comment.
OL,10,FThe two sides held multiple rounds of
OL,11,Ftalks last year that collapsed when
OL,12,FIsrael launched a 12-day war against
OL,13,FIran in June, and the US carried out
OL,14,Fheavy strikes on its nuclear sites,
OL,15,Fleaving much of Tehran's nuclear
OL,16,Fprogramme in ruins, even as the full
OL,17,Fextent of the damage remains unclear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
