OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has emphasised the
OL,7,FUK's support for diplomatic efforts
OL,8,Fbetween Washington and Tehran, amid
OL,9,Ftensions over the use of UK air bases
OL,10,Ffor potential US strikes on Iran.
OL,12,FThe government is understood to be
OL,13,Fblocking Trump's request to use the
OL,14,FDiego Garcia base in the Chagos
OL,15,FIslands in the event that he decides
OL,16,Fto launch a military campaign against
OL,17,FIran, due to concerns it would breach
OL,18,Finternational law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
