OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn a call on Thursday with Saudi
OL,12,Fleader Crown Prince Mohammed bin
OL,13,FSalman, the prime minister emphasised
OL,14,Fthe UK's support for diplomatic
OL,15,Fefforts.
OL,17,FA Downing Street spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"On Iran, the Prime Minister
OL,19,Femphasised the UK's focus remains on
OL,20,Fsupporting the political process
OL,21,Fongoing between the US and Iran.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
