OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,F"He added that Iran must never be able
OL,7,Fto develop a nuclear weapon and
OL,8,Fsecurity in the region must be a
OL,9,Fpriority."
OL,11,FIf America attacks, Iran has said US
OL,12,Fmilitary bases in the region would be
OL,13,Fconsidered legitimate targets, putting
OL,14,Fat risk tens of thousands of American
OL,15,Fservice members.
OL,17,FIran has also threatened to attack
OL,18,FIsrael, meaning a regional war again
OL,19,Fcould erupt across the Middle East.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
