OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,F"There would be no victory for anybody
OL,7,F- it would be a devastating war,"
OL,8,FAraghchi told India Today in an
OL,9,Finterview recorded Wednesday just
OL,10,Fbefore he flew to Geneva.
OL,12,F"Since the Americans' bases are
OL,13,Fscattered through different places in
OL,14,Fthe region, then unfortunately perhaps
OL,15,Fthe whole region would be engaged and
OL,16,Fbe involved, so it is a very terrible
OL,17,Fscenario."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]tD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
