OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772212805
OL,3,CUS-Iran nuclear talks wrap up without
OL,4,Ca deal as Trump weighs strike
OL,6,FAli Vaez, an Iran expert with the
OL,7,FInternational Crisis Group, said it
OL,8,Fwas a good sign that the Americans did
OL,9,Fnot walk away immediately on Thursday
OL,10,Fwhen Iran presented its latest
OL,11,Fproposal.
OL,13,F"There might still not be a
OL,14,Fbreakthrough at the end of this day,
OL,15,Fbut the very fact that the US team is
OL,16,Freturning shows that there is enough
OL,17,Fcommon ground between the two sides,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
